Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:14.53,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{They say seven out of ten high school\N couples break up within a year.}Người ta nói rằng 7 trên 10 cặp đôi\N cao trung sẽ chia tay trong vòng một năm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:19.79,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{If you include after graduation, \Nalmost all of them are destined to break up.}Nếu tính cả sau tốt nghiệp\N thì gần như tất cả đều chia tay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:25.83,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Ngay cả vậy, người ta vẫn vướng \Nvào tình yêu, khóc cười cùng nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:29.92,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I don't have a lot of confidence,\Nin reality or in myself,}Tôi không có nhiều tự tin, vào thực tại lẫn bản thân,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:34.49,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{that I'll ever find my world changed\N by a fleeting relationship like that.}rằng thế giới của mình sẽ thay đổi bởi một\N mối quan hệ thoáng qua như vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:39.33,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{But sometimes, I wonder.}Nhưng thỉnh thoảng tôi tự hỏi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:44.04,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{What if I actually did have an \Nexperience like that in my teens?}Nếu tôi thực sự có trải nghiệm đó ở tuổi trẻ thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:47.87,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{What if I did find a teary-eyed \Nheroine standing before me?}Điều gì xảy ra nếu tôi thấy một nữ chính \Nvới đôi mắt đẫm lệ trước mặt mình?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:51.82,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{What if I was the main \Ncharacter in a light novel?}Nếu tôi là nhân vật chính trong LN thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:54.28,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{If that happened...}Nếu điều đó xảy ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.44,0:00:57.25,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{what would I think about it?}thì tôi sẽ nghĩ gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:06.25,Flashback,Kurumi,0,0,0,,{You did your best, big brother!\NI know it must've been hard.}Anh đã cố hết sức rồi. Em biết mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:10.63,Italics,Kurumi & Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{"I know all about how dedicated you are."}Em biết anh đã rất cố gắng mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:14.37,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{"So if you need anyone to lean on, \Nyour little Kurumi is right here for you."}Nếu anh cần ai đó dựa vào thì Kurumi sẽ luôn có mặt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.52,0:01:24.84,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Oh, this is so good. \NAnd I'm finally about to get to the climax!}Quả nhiên là quá đã.\N Giờ thì đọc đến phần cao trào thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:28.73,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Every book in this series has twenty pages\Nof the lead getting totally pampered.}Mỗi quyển của bộ này đều có 20 trang mở đầu\N trước khi bước vào nội dung chính.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:29.44,Top,Anna,0,0,0,,{You can't, Sosuke!}Không được Sosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.66,0:01:32.48,Italics,Anna,0,0,0,,{You can't be wasting time like this!}Cậu không thể cứ phí thời gian như vậy được!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:33.15,Italics,Sosuke,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.47,0:01:37.00,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{They're in my class. \NThat's Yanami Anna and Hakamada Sosuke.}Học cùng lớp. Yanami Anna và Kakamada Sosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:40.66,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Why are they having a lovers' \Nquarrel in a place like this?}Sao lại cãi lộn ở đây vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:44.49,Top,Anna,0,0,0,,{If you don't go see her now, \NKaren-chan is gonna leave for England!}Nếu không gặp cậu ấy ngay, Karen sẽ đi Anh mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:45.93,Top,Anna,0,0,0,,Cậu thấy vậy ổn à?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:48.83,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Karen must be that girl \Nwho transferred recently.}Karen? Là người chuyển trường gần đây...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:52.26,Flashback,Karen,0,0,0,,{A-ha! You're that molester from before!}A, cậu là kẻ quấy rối lúc trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:54.76,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{She's already transferring again?\N And to England?}Lại chuyển trường nữa à? Lần này là Anh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:01:56.72,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{The story's moving way too fast!}Sao mà chuyển biến nhanh vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:02:00.81,Italics,Sosuke,0,0,0,,{But Karen... already said goodbye to me.}Nhưng Karen... đã tạm biệt tớ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:04.12,Italics,Anna,0,0,0,,{That obviously means she \Nwants you to go see her!}Ý cậu ấy muốn cậu đuổi theo đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:05.14,Italics,Sosuke,0,0,0,,{How would you know—}Sao cậu biết--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:06.05,Italics,Anna,0,0,0,,{Because I get it!}Tớ biết!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:11.40,Italics,Anna,0,0,0,,{I mean, that's how I've always \Nfelt about you, Sosuke.}Vì đó cũng là cảm xúc của tớ dành cho cậu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:14.01,Italics,Sosuke,0,0,0,,Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.01,Italics,Sosuke,0,0,0,,{I...}Tớ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:21.93,Italics,Anna,0,0,0,,{Go to her. Karen-chan's waiting for you.}Đến gặp cậu ấy đi. Karen đang chờ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:31.33,Italics,Sosuke,0,0,0,,{I'm so sorry.}Xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:39.30,Italics,Anna,0,0,0,,{Don't apologize to me, idiot.}Đừng có xin lỗi, đồ ngốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.67,0:02:43.31,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Maybe I'll just pretend \NI didn't see anything.}Giả vờ chưa thấy gì thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.93,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{N-No! Anything but that!}K-Không có lẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:03:01.09,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Stop! That's so painfully desperate!}Dừng lại! Chuyện như vậy... đừng mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:24.40,Default,Employee,0,0,0,,{Miss! Are you all right?}Quý khách ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:26.33,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I didn't see a thing.}Mình chưa thấy gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:38.88,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Sosuke and I have been friends\N since we were little.}Sosuke và tớ là bạn thuở nhỏ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.29,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Uh...}Ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:42.04,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{He made me a ring out of white clover.}Cậu ấy làm cho tớ chiếc nhẫn cỏ ba lá trắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:45.21,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{He said he'd make me his wife.}Và nói sẽ cưới tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:47.89,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{His wife.}Vợ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:53.13,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{His wife... His wife!}Vợ của cậu ấy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.13,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yanami-san, are you okay?!}Yanami, cậu ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.95,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{For now, just drink that \Nand try to calm down.}Tóm lại uống nước rồi bình tĩnh đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:03.93,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Thanks. You're in my class... \NNukumizu-kun, right?}Cảm ơn cậu... học cùng lớp Nukumizu nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:06.14,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Huh? You're asking me that now?}Hả? Giờ này mới hỏi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.10,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{This is really good.}Ngon ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:10.29,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{It's rosehip tea.}Là trà hoa hồng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:12.42,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{It's supposed to be good for the skin.}Nó tốt cho da lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:14.52,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{For my skin?}Tốt cho da?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.87,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I don't have anyone to show it off to.}Tớ cũng chẳng cần phải dưỡng da nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:19.23,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Stop! Too graphic for me!}Đừng nói mấy câu đó nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:21.65,Default,employee,0,0,0,,{Extra large fries. Here you are.}Khoai tây chiên loại lớn đây ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:22.77,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Yes, thank you!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:24.60,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{What? I didn't order that.}Hả? Mình có gọi món đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:28.20,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{You're fine with honey mustard \Nand cod roe mayo for sauces, right?}Cậu thích sốt mật ong và mayo nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.14,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Did you order that, Yanami-san?}Cậu gọi món hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:34.04,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Karen-chan's a dear friend of mine. But...}Karen là bạn thân của tớ nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:38.06,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{But you know, she just\N transferred here in May!}Nhưng cậu ấy chỉ mới chuyển đến tháng 5 thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:41.88,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Don't the twelve years I've known \NSosuke count for anything?}Còn tớ biết Sosuke tận 12 năm lận đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:46.17,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I'll ask one more time. \NWas it you who ordered the fries?}Tớ hỏi lại nhé, cậu gọi món hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:51.89,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Sosuke said he'd make me his wife. \NIsn't that mean? What a liar, right?}Sosuke nói sẽ lấy tớ làm vợ nữa chứ. Tên dối trá.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:54.85,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{When exactly did he say that?}Vụ đó từ khi nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:59.61,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{It was before elementary school, \Nso we must've been about four or five.}Từ hồi trước khi lên tiểu học, chắc cỡ 4,5 tuổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:00.65,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yeah, that doesn't count.}Ai mà tính cái đó hả...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:03.17,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Wait. Does this mean he's cheating on me?}Khoan, đây là lừa dối nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:05.75,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Were you and Hakamada actually dating?}Cậu và Hakamada hẹn hò hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.98,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Oh, gosh. I guess it probably looked that way.}Cậu trông giống thế hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:13.13,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{So you weren't even going out? \NThen it's not cheating at all!}Không hẹn hò thì làm gì có chuyện lừa dối?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:16.21,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I-I mean, it was basically like \Nwe were half-dating, though.}T-Thì... xem như là hẹn hò một nửa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:21.17,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{And if that soggy cow hadn't waltzed onto\N the scene, we'd probably still be together!}Và nếu con vú bò đó không xuất hiện \Nthì giờ có khi đang hẹn hò thật rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.83,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Wasn't she a "dear friend" a moment ago?}Ủa? Bạn thân mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:25.38,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{But I get it.}Nhưng tớ hiểu mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:30.58,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{If I'd worked up the courage sooner, \Nthings might not have turned out like this.}Nếu tớ chịu can đảm hơn thì đã...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:32.32,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{W-Well, you might be right.}À ừm, phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:35.01,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry I'm such a mess today.}Xin lỗi, hôm nay đúng là rối lên hết mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:36.82,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{No, it's totally fine.}À không sao...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:38.56,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{That's not what you need to apologize for.}Cậu không cần xin lỗi vì điều đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:40.78,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{But I'm okay with it.}Nhưng tớ chấp nhận rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:46.79,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{As long as Sosuke's happy, I'm okay with it.}Miễn Sosuke hạnh phúc là đủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:50.69,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{What a spectacular reaction \Nto getting rejected.}Cái phản ứng cao thượng khi bị từ chối này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:56.50,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Speaking of, there's a term that \Nperfectly describes girls like her.}Hình như có một câu mô tả những cô gái giống vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:06:00.83,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yanami Anna. Yes, it fits you perfectly.}Yanami Anna, đúng, cậu ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:01.92,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{You're a "losing heroine."}Là một nữ chính thua cuộc.
