Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:20.56,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Few realize that the flavor of water\N changes depending on the faucet.}Ít người nhận ra hương vị của nước thay đổi theo vòi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:23.70,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I am one of those who does.}Tôi thì biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:27.79,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{In the morning, the water from \Nthis faucet really is the best.}Quả nhiên nước sáng sớm là ngon nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:32.49,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{It's the farthest one from \Nthe water tank on the roof,}Nằm xa bể nước trên mái nhà nhất,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.86,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{so the water has a much \Nlower chlorine content.}nên nước sẽ có ít clo hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:40.39,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Once I've had my fill, I calculate the distance\N and time it'll take me to get back to class.}Sau khi uống xong, tôi tính quãng\N đường ngắn nhất để quay lại lớp học.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:46.05,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{If I get back too soon, I may find someone\N in my seat, and that'd be annoying.}Nếu quay lại sớm, sẽ có ai đó ngồi\N vào chỗ tôi và nó rất phiền phức.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.13,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Perfect.}Hoàn hảo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:50.88,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{But someone's in my seat.}Ơ, có ai đó đang ngồi chỗ mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:54.69,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Ah, shoot. I guess that explains it.}Chết. Hoá ra là tự học...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:53.85,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\an8\bord0\shad0\b1\fs16\frz7.747\pos(238,208.666)\c&HBBC0AF&}{4th Period: World History \Nwill start 10 minutes late.\NIndependent study \Nuntil then!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:04.91,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Huh. Looks like the archery team made it \Nto nationals for the third year in a row.}Có vẻ đội bắn cung lọt vào\N giải toàn quốc 3 năm liên tiếp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:07.22,Top,Karen,0,0,0,,{Okay, then the three of us \Nshould eat lunch together!}Vậy thì ba bọn mình ăn trưa cùng nhau đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:06.11,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Impressive.}Đỉnh thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:08.74,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna pass on that.}Tớ xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:13.34,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Sosuke, be sure to take \Ngood care of Karen-chan.}Sosuke, hãy chăm sóc Karen đàng hoàng vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:14.66,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.29,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,{You really are my best friend, Anna.}Cậu là bạn thân nhất của tớ nhỉ, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:22.05,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Even though she calls you a "soggy cow"?}Vậy mà cậu ta gọi cậu là vú bò đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:25.79,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Well, maybe Yanami's over it by now...}À thì... có vẻ Yanami đã vượt qua...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:28.63,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Wow. Yeah, she's not over anything yet.}Vẫn chưa vượt qua kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:33.72,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Hey, Yanami-san.}Nè Yanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:38.64,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{U-Um, you're on duty today, right?}Hôm nay cậu có nhiệm vụ mà nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:42.33,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Amanatsu-sensei's asking for you \Nto go help in the printing room.}Cô Amanatsu nhờ cậu vụ in ấn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:45.26,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Oh, really? I'm on my way.}Vậy hả? Tớ đến liền.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:50.57,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Nukumizu-kun, did you \Nsay that to help me out?}Nukumizu, cậu giúp tớ hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.57,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Well, kind of.}Đại loại.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:54.08,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Thanks.}Cảm ơn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:57.84,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Another second and I'd have had \Na death grip on Karen-chan's boobs.}Tí nữa thì tớ bóp nát cặp vú đó rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:59.79,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{How can she say that with a straight face?}Sao cậu ta nói nghe nghiêm túc vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:03.54,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Oh, by the way, remember \Nhow I paid for you on Friday?}À, hôm thứ 6 tớ có thanh toán cho cậu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.92,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Oh, yeah. Thanks for that.}A, cảm ơn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:11.83,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I don't have my wallet on me, but maybe you \Ncan meet me at the emergency stairs at lunch?}Giờ tớ không mang ví nên buổi trưa\N gặp tớ ở cầu thang thoát hiểm nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:12.80,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.26,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{The fire escape staircase. \NIn the old building.}Cầu thang thoát hiểm ở toà nhà cũ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:19.12,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Sure. As long as you pay me back.}Ừ, miễn là trả tiền.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:23.47,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{You know, they actually started dating.}Hai bọn họ đã hẹn hò rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:26.94,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{So why did they ask me to \Neat with them? It's so weird.}Vậy mà cứ muốn ăn cùng tớ. Lạ thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.89,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{And here I thought we were good friends.}Tớ tưởng bọn tớ là bạn thân.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:31.69,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I wonder if they're trying \Nto hurt me even more.}Họ tính làm tớ đau khổ hay gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:34.73,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Are you guys seriously best friends?}Mấy cậu thực sự là bạn thân à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:35.66,Top,Amanatsu,0,0,0,,{Hey! Yanami!}Nè Yanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.70,Default,Amanatsu,0,0,0,,{What are you doing? Class is about to st—}Làm gì thế hả? Lớp học bắt đầu rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:42.29,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Amana-chan, are you okay?}Amana-chan, ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.75,Default,Amanatsu,0,0,0,,{Ow, ow, ow. Thanks.}Đau... cảm ơn em.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:47.71,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Amanatsu-sensei, aren't these \Nthe wrong lesson materials?}Cô có mang lộn bài tập không vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:51.24,Default,Amanatsu,0,0,0,,{Hey, I don't know who you think you are,\N but get it together, man!}Này, cô không biết em là ai nhưng đừng có giỡn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:56.00,Default,Amanatsu,0,0,0,,{In second year, we cover the \NByzantine Empire! Viva Byzantine!}Trong năm thứ 2, chúng ta sẽ bao trùm đế \Nchế Byzantine! Viva Byzantine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:58.99,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Sensei, your next class is 1-C.}Cô ơi, tiếp sau là lớp 1-C.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:00.14,Default,Amanatsu,0,0,0,,{Huh?!}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:04.06,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{And I'm actually one \Nof your students, Sensei.}Và tôi là học sinh của lớp cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:04.75,Default,Amanatsu,0,0,0,,Byzantine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:06.10,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Not Byzantine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.08,Default,female student,0,0,0,,{Isn't that wild?}Đỉnh chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:22.24,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Please save me.}Cứu với.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:26.92,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Karen-chan wants the three of us to\Ngo do karaoke together after school.}Karen-chan muốn sau giờ học 3 đứa đi hát kara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:28.67,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{So why don't you?}Thì đi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:32.05,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Bắt tớ nghe hai người đó hát đôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:35.05,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Nukumizu-kun, are you \Nsaying you want me to die?}Nukumizu, cậu muốn giết tớ hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:38.47,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Well, no... Uh, good luck, I guess.}À ừm... thì... cố gắng lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:41.22,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{So about the money from before—}Về vụ tiền hôm bữa--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.10,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{That night...}Đêm đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:45.43,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I even got a message from Sosuke's sister.}Tớ nhận được tin nhắn của chị Sosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:49.65,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{"I can't get a hold of Sosuke. \NAre you two together?"}Chị không gọi được Sosuke,\N em đang ở cùng với nó hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:53.65,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Now, why in the world didn't\N he see her messages? I wonder.}Tại sao không gọi được nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:54.07,Italics Top,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Somebody save me.}Cứu tôi với.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:55.11,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I wonder.}Tại sao nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:56.49,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I wonder!}Lạ thật đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:00.52,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Sorry.}Xin lỗi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:04.58,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I can't talk about this with any \Nof my friends or acquaintances.}Tớ không thể nói chuyện này với người quen nào cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:07.29,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Guess that means I'm not\N even an acquaintance.}Vậy mình là người lạ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:12.04,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{So... do you think you can \Nfinally pay me back now?}Vậy thì trả tiền tớ được chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.05,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Here's the receipt from before.}Biên lai từ hôm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:18.23,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Yeah, thanks so much for that.\N You really saved my—}Cảm ơn cậu nhé. Lúc đó nhờ cậu--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:21.96,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Oh, my. Did the total go up?}Ủa? Sao có vẻ nhiều tiền vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:25.30,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yanami-san, you also got an order\N of watermelon pancakes, remember?}Yanami, cậu gọi thêm một bánh pancake dưa hấu nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:25.92,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Uh-huh.}Ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:28.54,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{And you finished up with\N a pork shabu udon salad.}Và kết thúc bằng một udon thịt heo kèm salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:30.58,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{'Cause salads don't make you gain weight.}Vì salad không gây tăng cân...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:34.02,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I'm not opposed to your faith\N in salads. Not at all.}Tớ không phản đối điều đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:39.53,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{It's just an idea, but what if I were \Nto repay you in some other way?}Ví dụ thôi... có thể trả bằng cách khác không?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:40.94,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Some other way?}Cách khác?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:48.66,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I'm not actually very good at it, \Nso I'm not sure if it'll satisfy you,}Tớ không giỏi lắm, không biết cách làm cậu hài lòng...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:52.46,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{but Sosuke used to say he really liked it.}nhưng Sosuke nói cậu ấy thích lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:53.81,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Huh? What?!}Hả? Cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:56.51,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{She can't possibly mean \Ndoing something wet and sticky!}Không lẽ cậu ấy tính làm gì đó ướt át và nhớp nháp?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:59.42,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Không ổn! Đang ở trường mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.34,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I...}Tớ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.30,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Listen—}Nghe nè--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.69,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I'm not very good at cooking, \Nbut I think I could manage a bento lunch!}Tớ không giỏi nấu ăn nhưng chỉ là bento thì có thể!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.05,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{A bento lunch?}Bento?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:09.37,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Something wrong?}Sao? Có gì hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:11.64,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Oh, right! A bento lunch!}A, bento nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:14.29,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{But one bento lunch \Nprobably won't cover it...}Nhưng một hộp thì sao đủ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:18.50,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Right, so I'll make you one every day \Nuntil it equals the amount on the receipt.}Thế nên tớ sẽ làm cho cậu đến khi nào đủ tiền.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:19.86,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:22.33,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Okay, we'll start tomorrow.\N I'll be waiting here.}Vậy thì bắt đầu từ mai luôn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:27.66,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Sure.}Ừm.
