Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:12.85,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{I heard you joined the lit club, Nukumizu.}Nghe nói cậu tham gia CLB văn học?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:16.88,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{My teacher told me they have \Nthe complete works of Abe Kobo.}Giáo viên nói rằng họ có \Ntoàn bộ tác phẩm của Abe Kobo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:18.70,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Can I borrow them sometime?}Tớ mượn được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:23.42,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Oh, uh, that's probably okay. \NI'll check with my senpai.}Tớ nghĩ là được. Để tớ hỏi lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:23.92,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Thanks.}Cảm ơn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:25.63,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:30.34,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{I'm skipping my club today. \NWanna go get something to eat?}Hôm nay tớ trốn CLB, đi ăn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:32.69,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Sorry. I have prep school today.}Xin lỗi, nay tớ phải đi học thêm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:34.94,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Huh? You're still a first-year.}Hả? Mới năm 1 mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:38.14,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{If all you do is study, \Nyou're just gonna get dumber.}Nếu học hoài vậy sẽ thành thằng ngu đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:41.63,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{And if you don't study more, \Nyou'll end up repeating the year.}Nếu cậu không học thêm là bị đúp đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:46.06,Default,Chihaya,0,0,0,,{Mitsuki-san. We're going to be late \Nto cram school if we don't get going.}Mitsuki, chúng ta sẽ trễ giờ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:48.65,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{Oh, Chihaya. I'm coming.}A, Chihaya. Đến đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:50.24,Default,Ayano,0,0,0,,{See you later, Lemon.}Vậy gặp sau nhé Lemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:53.16,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Huh? Oh... Bye-bye.}Hả? Ừm... chào nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:58.25,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Hey, are you and Mitsuki friends?}Cậu với Mitsuki là bạn hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:02.96,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Uh, we're not exactly friends, \Nbut we go to the same cram school—}À không hẳn... nhưng bọn tớ học thêm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:05.17,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{So do you know who that girl was?}Vậy cậu biết con nhỏ lúc nãy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:08.60,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Um, Asagumo-san, I think?}À... Asagumo hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:10.81,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{She and Ayano are both\Ntaking the advanced course.}Cậu ấy và Ayano học lớp nâng cao.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:12.70,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Advanced course, huh?}Nâng cao...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:17.68,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{I guess Mitsuki's into smart girls after all.}Mitsuki thích mấy bạn thông minh nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:19.84,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Lemon-chan, what are your intentions?}Lemon, cậu ấy là gì của cậu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:22.19,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Huh? N-Nothing.}K-Không có gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:25.80,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{It's just, we've been in the same \Nclass since elementary school...}Chỉ là bạn học chung từ tiểu học...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:27.37,Top,Anna,0,0,0,,{Sounds like you're childhood friends.}Bạn thuở nhỏ à.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:29.45,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Which means...}Tức là...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:31.90,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{That woman is the homewrecker.}Con nhỏ đó là... trà xanh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:33.82,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Oh, come on. "Homewrecker"?}Trà xanh á?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:38.93,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Listen, Nukumizu-kun, \Nthere are only two types of girls.}Nè Nukumizu, con gái chia làm 2 loại.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:41.20,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{The childhood friend and the homewrecker.}Bạn thuở nhỏ và trà xanh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.29,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I see.}À ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.83,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{But what a contrast!}Nghe có lý...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:46.98,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Hey, what do those two look like to you?}Nè, cậu thấy bọn họ sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:51.09,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{They seem pretty friendly, \Nbut didn't they meet just recently?}Nhìn có vẻ khá thân thiện\Nnhưng họ mới biết nhau mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:55.18,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Maybe they're just plain friends.}Chắc chỉ là bạn thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:58.61,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Right! I'm sure they're just plain friends!}Phải nhỉ! Chỉ là bạn thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:01.43,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{I knew you'd get it, Yana-chan!}Quả nhiên cậu hiểu rõ ghê, Yana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:05.26,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Lemon-chan, I kinda feel like \Nwe're not that different after all.}Lemon-chan, tớ cảm giác chúng ta sẽ là bạn thân đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.81,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I'm rooting for you!}Tớ cổ vũ cho cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:12.15,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{They're asking me to hang out again today.}Họ lại gọi tớ đi cùng hôm nay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:15.13,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{"Wanna come study at Karen-chan's house?"}Muốn đến nhà Karen-chan học không?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.49,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{You should say no.}Thì từ chối đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:19.98,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{But if I don't go, \Nit'll be just the two of them!}Nhưng nếu không đi là\N chỉ có bọn họ thôi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:22.62,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{That may be true, but where's my lunch?}Thì đúng... cơ mà bữa trưa đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:26.57,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Nukumizu-kun, you ever think this \Nmight be why you don't have friends?}Nukumizu, đó là lý do cậu không có bạn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:27.71,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I don't need that from you.}Không cần cậu lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:29.74,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Hold the lid a minute.}Cầm hộ cái nắp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:38.24,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I only have one lunch box I can use, \Nso I shoved the two servings into one box.}Vì chỉ dùng được 1 hộp cơm nên\N tớ đã nhét cả hai phần vào đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:40.09,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Okay, let's eat.}Ăn thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:44.30,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Nukumizu-kun, how much is that worth?}Nukumizu, giá bao nhiêu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:47.28,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Um, let's say 400 yen.}À thì... 400 yên.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:48.97,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Nice! Not bad at all.}Ngon, cũng không tệ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:52.64,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{At this rate, I should be able to \Npay it off by summer vacation.}Cứ thế này thì trả hết trước khi nghỉ hè rồi.
